The entire Opposition rose as Chief Minister Pramod Sawant asked Monserrate to keep reading the note.

â€œAs much as this law is unconstitutional, what you are doing is also unconstitutional. Do not come under pressure from the ruling party. You are murdering democracy. This is decitizenation too,â€ Sardesai told the Speaker.

